class Solution {
    public boolean makeStringsEqual(String s, String target) {
        int onesInS = 0, onesInTarget = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == '1') onesInS++;
            if (target.charAt(i) == '1') onesInTarget++;
        }
        return onesInS == 0 && onesInTarget == 0 || onesInS == s.length();
    }
}
```

efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(1)
